80
00:04:44,066 --> 00:04:47,266
<c.Japanese>（<c.Japanese>小田</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>おだ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>）まあ その辺のことは
