85
00:04:56,533 --> 00:04:57,733
<c.Japanese>宮本</c.Japanese>

86
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:02,566
<c.Japanese>逃げとったら商売できへんで</c.Japanese>

87
00:05:03,466 --> 00:05:05,033
